      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle exhibits flawless aesthetic and mechanical integrity, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector. Every detail, from the pristine upholstery to the immaculate engine bay, reflects a history of uncompromising care. We invite serious inquiries to inspect a vehicle that remains in its original, showroom-delivered state.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
